	Nicolas action    
	 Los Angeles, Dec. 15 (PTI): Actor Nicolas Cage is all set to play a reformed conman in action adventure Medallion. The project, to be directed by Simon West, has been in development for some time.       
	The movie revolves around a father, a former master thief, who has only a few hours to find his daughter when she is kidnapped and locked in the trunk of a New York medallion taxi cab, Hollywood Reporter said.     
	Swift day     
	 Los Angeles (PTI): Country star Taylor Swift spent her 21st birthday working in the studio and cut a pizza instead of a celebratory cake. The Love Story hitmaker ringed in her birthday with two friends who came with party hats and a pizza topped with candles but was left alone to dance to her favourite songs by Pink.
                                                                                                                                                      
